com.gensym.jgi
Class G2Version

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--com.gensym.jgi.G2Version
public class G2Version
extends Object

A class that encapsulates the version for a product (currently G2 and GSI?). It can be used to determine if a particular G2Version matches a minimum version.x
